column2: b'Kinnikuman: Kessen! Shichinin no Choujin tai Uchuu Nobushi'

b'A TV Special first aired in 1984. It covers the Planet Rakka story arc and takes place after the 21st Choujin Olympics Arc. A young boy from Planet Rakka named Beansman asks Kinnikuman and the others to help save his planet from the Space Samurais led by Black King. The story was a parody of The Seven Samurai.\n\n(Source: Kinnikuman Wiki)'
